name: CalciumAndVitaminDForMaleUrologyCare
title: Calcium and Vitamin D for male urology care
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains oral calcium and vitamin D medications taken for treatment of osteoporosis and/or osteopenia with prostate cancer patients undergoing androgen deprivation therapy.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify appropriate oral medications which contain calcium and vitamin D for the treatment of osteoporosis and/or osteopenia for men with prostate cancer.),(Inclusion Criteria: Oral drug forms of calcium and vitamin D appropriate for men with prostate cancer.),(Exclusion Criteria: Drug specified for females only.  Injectible drugs of calcium or vitamin D.)
